---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="DTL 2024">
	<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-neutral-900">
		<h1 class="text-5xl p-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-sky-600 text-transparent bg-clip-text">
			Design Thinking Lab - 2024
		</h1>

		<h2 class="text-2xl text-neutral-500">
			Digital Humanities
		</h2>

		<div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-8 max-w-screen-md">
			<p>
				The problem we aim to address is the limited reach and lack of impressions
				created from traditional, mass, cold emails.
			</p>
			<p>
				Students have been sending DTL forms en-masse with little to no personalization.
				This is influenced due to sociological and psychological factors. 
			</p>
			<p>
				Our hypothesis is that a little personalization can go a long way in creating
				a lasting impression and increasing the response rate.
			</p>
		</div>

		<hr class="my-4 h-1 max-w-screen-md w-full bg-white">

	</div>
</Layout>
